{"tid":825761,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"每日傾電話代表咩？","createTime":"2018-09-17T18:47:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T19:53:49.000Z","uid":210811,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e2dfeafb25d75138faa88c0d0257f236c1c9f8e3","tid":825761,"uid":210811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T18:47:18.000Z","msg":"對呢個男仔嘅行為有少少疑惑<br />\n第一次開post...有錯請輕手啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能有少少長<br />\n<br />\n我同佢係玩手機game識嘅<br />\n有見過幾次 成班人一齊食飯同單獨都有<br />\n佢好早移民左去溫哥華 上次見面係新年<br />\n本身無咩點講過野 <br />\n但佢對上果次番左香港有一齊打機<br />\n之後就開始有whatsapp傾計 傾左個幾月<br />\n有次佢就問可唔可以傾電話<br />\n跟住就開始左呢個習慣<br />\n原本以為佢番左溫哥華華就唔會再傾<br />\n因為有時差 點知佢都係keep住每日打黎<br />\n直至依家都差不多半年<br />\n<br />\n好多時佢會係香港時間11點左右打黎（佢果邊8點）<br />\n明明未瞓醒都會打黎 我就聽佢瞓覺 到醒左先傾<br />\n瞓前有時都會打黎 叫我聽到佢瞓就收線<br />\n之後醒又會再打黎....<br />\n<br />\n平時多數係傾閒計 無咩flirt嘅成份<br />\n佢目前單身 成日都會同我討論其他女仔<br />\n我都會同佢傾下其他男仔（我嘅追求者？<br />\n我知目前同佢係無可能<br />\n因為佢唔中意longd 同埋要又叻又靚嘅女仔<br />\n(應該係因為唔夠靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n但我諗至少有一點點嘅好感？<br />\n因為啲人成日話男仔唔中意傾電話？<br />\n以我了解 佢同其他人講野係好唔耐煩<br />\n唔會成日覆人果種<br />\n所以我真係睇唔透<br />\n佢係真係為無聊而傾 定係點<br />\n 求點醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"a38dffcb390e607a9d7ecf5b6685d03858649993","tid":825761,"uid":200672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T18:55:27.000Z","msg":"應該有d 野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔唔鐘意佢 我都唔會日日同佢傾電話啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"575481c4ba471dbd0a89b0255311baf1732c6a1b","tid":825761,"uid":200672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T18:56:01.000Z","msg":"或者可能佢喺個邊悶呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c712343994578d763ae68c7cc1a2dcf10a3b9128","tid":825761,"uid":431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T19:00:13.000Z","msg":"用唔晒啲分鐘"},{"pid":"73feeb20dd51a43ef4d4c0eb53be9ebf3d09b462","tid":825761,"uid":210811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a38dffcb390e607a9d7ecf5b6685d03858649993","tid":825761,"uid":200672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T18:55:27.000Z","msg":"應該有d 野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔唔鐘意佢 我都唔會日日同佢傾電話啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T19:02:22.000Z","msg":"有時會試探地問下有冇可能<br />\n佢都模糊地答 <br />\n不過目前應該只係朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d599b36e5dd8c426fa011b452ed0019515eda864","tid":825761,"uid":200672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73feeb20dd51a43ef4d4c0eb53be9ebf3d09b462","tid":825761,"uid":210811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a38dffcb390e607a9d7ecf5b6685d03858649993","tid":825761,"uid":200672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T18:55:27.000Z","msg":"應該有d 野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔唔鐘意佢 我都唔會日日同佢傾電話啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T19:02:22.000Z","msg":"有時會試探地問下有冇可能<br />\n佢都模糊地答 <br />\n不過目前應該只係朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T19:03:18.000Z","msg":"慘被friend-zone<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d3779bb48f6ec7befa813c7192d48d37f80c05","tid":825761,"uid":210811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c712343994578d763ae68c7cc1a2dcf10a3b9128","tid":825761,"uid":431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T19:00:13.000Z","msg":"用唔晒啲分鐘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T19:03:44.000Z","msg":"用whatsapp c